# UI Component Refinement Instructions for AI Coding Assistant

## Overall Design Philosophy

We need to modernize these UI components to feel less "bubbly" and more professional. The current design uses too much border radius (10-12px) and loose spacing, making it feel playful rather than sophisticated. We want a tighter, more refined aesthetic that feels like a professional data management tool.

**Core Changes:**
- Reduce border radius from 10-12px down to 6-8px throughout
- Tighten padding and spacing (reduce by 20-30%)
- Use more sophisticated gray color palette
- Add subtle shadows instead of heavy borders
- Improve typography hierarchy with varied sizes and weights
- Make hover states more subtle and refined

---

## Component 1: Popup Field Visibility Modal

### Goal
Transform the field visibility configuration modal from a bubbly, loose layout into a tight, professional interface. Each field card should feel compact but still breathable. The controls should be inline and efficient.

### Specific HTML/CSS Changes

**Modal Container:**
```css
/* CHANGE FROM: */
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 24px;

/* CHANGE TO: */
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 20px 24px;
```

**Field Cards:**
```css
/* CHANGE FROM: */
.field-card {
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
}

/* CHANGE TO: */
.field-card {
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    transition: all 0.2s;
}

.field-card:hover {
    border-color: #cbd5e1;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
}
```

**Field Type Labels:**
```css
/* ADD NEW: */
.field-type {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #64748b;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: 500;
}
```

**Control Groups:**
```css
/* CHANGE FROM: */
.control-group {
    gap: 10px;
}

/* CHANGE TO: */
.control-group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
}

.control-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #475569;
    font-weight: 500;
}
```

**Select/Input Elements:**
```css
/* CHANGE FROM: */
select, input {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

/* CHANGE TO: */
select, input {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
}

select:focus, input:focus {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
}
```

