### Specific HTML/CSS Changes

**Sort Rule:**
```html
<div class="sort-rule">
    <div class="sort-handle">#1</div>
    <select>
        <option>Priority</option>
    </select>
    <select>
        <option>Ascending</option>
        <option>Descending</option>
    </select>
    <div class="sort-actions">
        <button class="btn-ghost">‚ñ≤</button>
        <button class="btn-ghost">‚ñº</button>
        <button class="btn-ghost">‚úï</button>
    </div>
</div>
```

```css
.sort-rule {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

