## Component 7: Buttons

### Goal
Make buttons feel more modern and refined with better hover states and less rounded corners.

### Specific HTML/CSS Changes

```css
/* CHANGE FROM: */
.btn {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

/* CHANGE TO: */
.btn {
    padding: 9px 18px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
}

.btn-primary {
    background: #0f172a;
    color: white;
    border-color: #0f172a;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1e293b;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #475569;
    border-color: #cbd5e1;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-color: #94a3b8;
}

.btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: #475569;
    border: none;
}

.btn-ghost:hover {
    background: #f1f5f9;
}

.btn-sm {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
}
```

