## Universal Color Palette

Replace all color values with this refined palette:

```css
/* REPLACE OLD COLORS WITH: */
--primary: #0f172a;
--primary-hover: #1e293b;
--accent: #3b82f6;
--accent-light: #eff6ff;

--text-primary: #0f172a;
--text-secondary: #475569;
--text-muted: #64748b;
--text-disabled: #94a3b8;

--border: #e2e8f0;
--border-hover: #cbd5e1;
--border-strong: #94a3b8;

--surface: #ffffff;
--surface-hover: #f8fafc;
--surface-muted: #f1f5f9;
--background: #fafbfc;
```

---

## Summary Checklist

For each component, ensure:
- [ ] Border radius reduced to 6-8px (from 10-12px)
- [ ] Padding reduced by 20-30%
- [ ] Font sizes use the new scale (11px, 12px, 13px, 14px, 16px, 20px)
- [ ] Colors updated to refined gray palette
- [ ] Hover states are subtle with smooth transitions
- [ ] Focus states include blue ring with 3px shadow
- [ ] Gaps between elements use 8px, 12px, or 16px (not 10px, 15px, 20px)
- [ ] Icons included where appropriate for visual identification
- [ ] Typography weights varied (500, 600 for emphasis)
- [ ] Shadows are subtle (0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04) for hover)
